name: Transtemporal tingle
description: We have the chance to create something that humanity dreamt of or thought it is impossible to happen. Many theoretician have studied the subject how to preserve something that is affected by time. The metaverse has opened the doors for creating that archive, without the data being lost.  But this doesn't mean that we have reached the peak. As long as the destructive forces of the material world exist, we have to search the answers even further on the next meta level.
